data.description: 3 BEDROOM + DEDICATED OFFICE. This Amelia Floor plan 2018 Mattamy offers a beautiful and customized living experience like no other. With Phillips HUE lighting installed throughout the house, you can easily control and automate the lighting using a simple app at your fingertips. WYZE cameras are also integrated with security panel and work with ALEXA on command, allowing you to monitor and have full control of your home's connectivity for ease of use. One of the standout features of this home is the full house generator, providing backup power to ensure that your utilities are always running even during power outages. This is especially convenient and useful in case of emergencies. Fully fenced yard (fence) installed in 2020 with plenty of room for your pets to enjoy those sunny days with room for you to install a pool if you so choose. For those who work from home, there is a dedicated office space with large window views allowing for a comfortable and productive work environment. Guest bedrooms offer sizeable space for your favorite furniture and easy flow. The kitchen is a highlight of the home, with beautiful white cabinets that complement the custom granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The open and bright kitchen receives plenty of natural light, providing an inviting and pleasant atmosphere for cooking and entertaining. In the owner's suite you'll find tray ceilings that add a touch of elegance. The spacious walk-in closet offers plenty of storage space, and the en-suite bathroom features a glass shower, framed mirrors, dual sinks with custom granite countertops to enjoy your own private oasis. Minutes to Tampa and waterways for boating! A brand-new ADVENT Health hospital minutes away due to open in 2024. Many restaurants and waterfront dining to experience. This community offer a resort style pool, clubhouse, playground and pond views. Locating right in Riverview, Florida the growing suburb of TAMPA. We are growing, come grow with US! Some photos are virtually staged.
